data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. HUGE PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!! Bring your fur babies! Lovely, gated community of Countryside Key is located right in the center of it all. Darling townhome has all you need to live the maintenance-free, Florida lifestyle. Enter through the front door to a spacious living and dining area with soaring ceilings, along with a half bath downstairs for extra convenience.  Kitchen features black, SS appliances, stationary island, laminate backsplash, and resurfaced countertops. Extra-large washer and dryer convey and are tucked away in a closet off kitchen. Enjoy private time out the back slider that leads to the screened in porch. No rear neighbors! Both bedrooms are located upstairs and share a large, serene-like spa bathroom, tucked behind a barn door. Newer, double vanity and granite countertop accompany the tiled, oversized shower and bathtub. En-suite bath connects to the primary bedroom which has double closets with organizers, plus an extra closet for linens and more storage. Low, monthly fees cover water, sewer, and trash, cable and internet, exterior maintenance and roof. For just an extra $25 a month, enjoy recreational storage for your RV, boat, or trailer. Picturesque community features tennis courts, pool, car washing station, and plenty of room to walk your dog. Just minutes from shopping, dining, airport, parks, golf courses, movie theaters, and so much more! HVAC 2021, water heater 2020. Seller says furniture conveys! Bring your clothes and move right in!
